{{tt|acw|طاولة|f|tr=ṭāwla}}\n*: Iraqi Arabic: {{tt|acm|ميز|f|tr=mēz}}, {{tt|ar|منضدة|f|tr=minḍade}}\n*: Juba Arabic: {{t|pga|tarabeeza}}\n*: Moroccan Arabic: {{tt|ary|طابلة|f|tr=ṭābla}}, {{tt|ary|طبلة|f|tr=ṭabla}}, {{tt|ary|ميدة|f|tr=mīda}}, {{tt|ary|طاولة|f|tr=ṭāwla}}\n*: North Levantine Arabic: {{tt|apc|طاولة|f|tr=ṭāwle}} {{q|Lebanon}}\n*: Yemeni Arabic: {{tt|ayn|مايده|f|tr=maydeh}} {{q|Sanaa}}\n* Armenian: {{tt+|hy|սեղան}}\n* Aromanian: {{tt|rup|measã|f}}\n* Assamese: {{tt|as|মেজ}}, {{tt|as|টেবুল}}\n* Asturian: {{tt+|ast|mesa|f}}\n* Azerbaijani: {{tt+|az|stol}}, {{tt+|az|masa}}\n* Baba Malay: {{tt|mbf|toh}}\n* Bashkir: {{tt|ba|өҫтәл}}\n* Basque: {{tt+|eu|mahai}}\n* Belarusian: {{tt+|be|стол|m}}\n* Bengali: {{tt+|bn|টেবিল}}, {{tt+|bn|মেজ}}\n* Breton: {{tt+|br|taol}}\n* Bulgarian: {{tt+|bg|ма́са|f}}\n* Burmese: {{tt+|my|စားပွဲ}}\n* Buryat: {{t|bua|стол}}\n* Carpathian Rusyn: {{tt|rue|стул|m}}\n* Catalan: {{tt+|ca|taula|f}}\n* Cebuano: {{t|ceb|lamesa}}, {{t|ceb|talad}}\n* Chagatai: {{tt|chg|شِیرَهْ|tr=šīräh}}\n* Chakma: {{t-needed|ccp}}\n* Chamicuro: {{tt|ccc|mesa}}\n* Chechen: {{t|ce|стол}}\n* Cherokee: {{tt|chr|ᎦᏍᎩᎶ}}\n* Cheyenne: {{t|chy|táxemésėhestȯtse}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Cantonese: {{tt|yue|檯}}, {{tt|yue|枱|tr=toi4-2}}\n*: Dungan: {{tt|dng|җуәзы}}\n*: Eastern Min: {{t|cdo|桌|tr=dŏ̤}}\n*: Hokkien: {{tt+|nan-hbl|桌仔|tr=toh-á}}, {{tt+|nan-hbl|桌|tr=toh}}\n*: Mandarin: {{tt+|cmn|桌子|tr=zhuōzi}}\n*: Wu: {{tt|wuu|檯子}}\n* Chuvash: {{tt|cv|сӗтел}}\n* Comorian:\n*: Ngazidja Comorian: {{tt|zdj|meza|c9|c10}}, {{tt|zdj|ulio|c11}}, {{tt|zdj|latabu|c9|c10}}\n* Comox: {{tt|coo|θewθeytən}}\n* Coptic:\n*: Bohairic Coptic: {{tt|cop|ⲧⲣⲁⲡⲉⲍⲁ|f}}, {{tt|cop|ⲫⲟⲣϣⲓ|f}}\n*: Sahidic Coptic: {{tt|cop|ⲧⲣⲁⲡⲉⲍⲁ|f}}, {{tt|cop|ⲡⲟⲣϣⲥ|f}}\n* Cornish: {{tt|kw|moos|f}}, {{tt|kw|bordh|m}}\n* Crimean Tatar: {{tt|crh|masa}}, {{tt|crh|sofra}}\n* Czech: {{tt+|cs|stůl|m}}\n* Dalmatian: {{tt|dlm|maisa|f}}\n* Danish: {{tt+|da|bord|n}}\n* Dhivehi: {{tt|dv|މޭޒު}}\n* Dongxiang: {{tt|sce|shire}}\n* Drung: {{tt|duu